==Mission-Specific==
===Friend, the case is closed.===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' Friend, the case is closed.
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Go on.
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Love to hear it.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' The Ruff Tape was the killer, not the victim.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' He lured the boss with the excuse of giving him the evidence and killed him.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' With the loud music, the witnesses all assumed the tape was the victim.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' Of course, aside from the sounds they play, all the tapes in Penacony look the same.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' Finally, he put his boss's tape inside himself, stealing the other's sound and identity before fleeing the scene.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' The key clue was that the tape inside his body had been fixed before.
:{Choice} What about the boss' secret?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Even in the end, I have no clue what his boss had on him.
::'''Billboard Investigator:''' Ah, don't think about that stuff.
:{Choice} That's one vicious tape.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' They're supposed to be cassette tapes. How could they be so cruel?
::'''Billboard Investigator:''' That's why we're needed.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' It was all thanks to your help this time, otherwise the truth would've been lost forever.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' Looking forward to working with you again in the future.
}}
