===Sorry, I didn't find...===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' Sorry, I didn't find the killer in the end.
:'''Billboard Investigator:''' There just weren't enough clues at the scene. I plan to investigate the victim's whereabouts leading up to their deaths.
:{Choice} I'll wait for your good news.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When you crack the case, call me first so we can celebrate together.
::'''Billboard Investigator:''' Alright, it's a deal, then.
:{Choice} Stay safe.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The criminal is a vicious one. Be careful when conducting your investigation.
::'''Billboard Investigator:''' I will. Thanks for the concern.
}}
